<HL>
   Corroon's Stock
   Plunges as Aon
   Backs Off Its Bid
   ----
   By James P. Miller and Richard E. Rustin
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/20/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
